hopobject.body: A staff restaurant buysupplement.org There are those who argue that not abridging the right to keep and bear arms should be limited to flintlock smooth bore muskets. But it is an absurd, laughable assertion. Liberty from unreasonable, and unreasoning, State intrusion into our lives is supposedly what millions of Americans have died for. Of course dictatorships have many fewer violent crimes than free countries. But freedom is what we were born to and freedom is what we want. Who cares what some General wants? Do your job, which is to defend our liberty.
